name: Face It
description: This piece explores the concept of assuming identities to start our the day. It is a coping mechanism; a mask of attitude that we put on before we head out into the world."Face It" is featured in iDENTITY | 02 | BIT.SHES Collection. All proceeds from this piece go to charitable organizations making a difference for positive change. Check out bitshes.com for more info!
